info.title: SAP IESS Object Storage Trusted (L2) Datastore API
info.summary: Output port di tipo Object Storage di livello 2 (trusted) su Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2 per data product SAP IESS

definition.name: vbep
definition.description: Tabella di "Sales Document: Schedule Line Data" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELN (Sales Document), POSNR (Sales Document Item), ETENR (Delivery Schedule Line Number), ETTYP (Schedule line category).

definition.name: vbrk
definition.description: Tabella di "Billing Document: Header Data" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELN (Billing Document), FKART (Billing Type), FKTYP (Billing category), VBTYP (SD document category).

definition.name: vbap
definition.description: Tabella di "Sales Document: Item Data" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELN (Sales Document), POSNR (Sales Document Item), MATNR (Material Number), MATWA (Material Entering).

definition.name: vbfa
definition.description: Tabella di "Sales Document Flow" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELV (Preceding sales and distribution document), POSNV (Preceding item of an SD document), VBELN (Subsequent sales and distribution document), POSNN (Subsequent item of an SD document).

definition.name: vbpa
definition.description: Tabella di "Sales Document: Partner" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELN (Sales and Distribution Document Number), POSNR (Item number del documento SD), PARVW (Partner Function), KUNNR (Customer Number).

definition.name: vbak
definition.description: Tabella di "Sales Document: Header Data" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELN (Sales Document), ERDAT (Date on Which Record Was Created), ERZET (Entry time), ERNAM (Name of Person who Created the Object).

definition.name: vbrp
definition.description: Tabella di "Billing Document: Item Data" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELN (Billing Document), POSNR (Billing item), UEPOS (Higher-level item in bill of material structures), FKIMG (Actual Invoiced Quantity).

definition.name: vbuk
definition.description: Tabella di "Sales Document: Header Status" e di "Administrative Data" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELN (Sales and Distribution Document Number), RFSTK (Reference document header status), RFGSK (Total reference status of all items), BESTK (Confirmation status).

definition.name: vbkd
definition.description: Tabella di "Sales Document: Business Data" disponibile su SAP R/3. Composta da vari campi, tra cui VBELN (Sales and Distribution Document Number), POSNR (Item number of the SD document), KONDA (Price group (customer)), KDGRP (Customer group).
